          "name": "t:names.text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>You can spot a MWL bride a mile away, she’s the first one to eat the cake, and the last one off the dance floor. She is a sucker for romance, the kind full of belly aching laughs and undeniable chemistry, the kind you can only find in a best friend. She loves giggling with girlfriends over cocktails, spending summer days at the beach and kicking up her heels with loved ones, all in equal measures, of course. She is unabashedly herself and dreams of finding a dress that matches up to her effortlessly chic, beautiful, confident self.</p>",
